misc: armchina-npu: default to the R2P0 userspace ABI

CIX packages cix-noe-umd 2.0.2 from the R2P0 SDK, while the imported
kernel driver implements the newer R2P2 ABI.  Port the vendor packaging
revert while retaining the local lifetime, ACPI DMA, SCMI devfreq, and
runtime-PM fixes.

The 19f2947 import stores its v3.2 register definitions in v3_1.h although
the driver includes v3_2.h.  Add a compatibility header for the imported
layout and apply the R2P0 debug-dispatch macro conversion to the real
definition file.

